# agent-booster — Environment Variables
#
# The agent-booster CLI itself needs NO environment variables and makes NO API calls.
# It is a zero-LLM, deterministic, fully offline tool. You can run it with no .env at all.
#
# The variables below are ONLY for the optional agent-native harness layer
# (.claude/, .mcp.json) — not for the CLI. Leave them unset unless you use those tools.
# Copy this file to .env (which is gitignored) if you need them.

# GitHub token for the harness's GitHub MCP server (.mcp.json) — optional.
# Get at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN=
